@startuml
title ATM State Transition Diagram

[*] --> PINEntry

state PINEntry
PINEntry : entry / card inserted
PINEntry : do / prompt user to enter PIN
PINEntry : exit / PIN entered

PINEntry --> PINVerification

state PINVerification
PINVerification : entry / PIN entered
PINVerification : do / verify PIN against stored information
PINVerification : exit / PIN verified or not

PINVerification --> Verified : [PIN verified]
PINVerification --> NotVerified : [PIN not verified]

state Verified
Verified : entry / PIN verified
Verified : do / provide options to user
Verified : do / process withdrawal request
Verified : exit / transaction completed

Verified --> CashDispensing : [Withdrawal request]

state CashDispensing
CashDispensing : entry / withdrawal request
CashDispensing : do / dispense cash
CashDispensing : exit / cash dispensed

CashDispensing --> ReceiptPrinting : [Cash dispensed]

state ReceiptPrinting
ReceiptPrinting : entry / cash dispensed
ReceiptPrinting : do / print receipt
ReceiptPrinting : exit / receipt printed

ReceiptPrinting --> CardReturn : [Receipt printed]

state CardReturn
CardReturn : entry / receipt printed
CardReturn : do / return user's card
CardReturn : exit / transaction completed

CardReturn --> Reset : [Card returned]

state Reset
Reset : entry / card returned
Reset : do / reset system
Reset : exit / system reset

Reset --> [*]

state NotVerified
NotVerified : entry / PIN not verified
NotVerified : do / prompt user to re-enter PIN
NotVerified : exit / PIN re-entered

NotVerified --> PINVerification : [PIN re-entered]

@enduml
